		   <h2 class="section-title">History</h2>
		  </div>

		      <div class="gallery">
			
			
			   
				<a href="aubin.html" class="gallery-item">
				  <div class="gallery-item-img" style="background-image:url(https://iiif-cloud.princeton.edu/iiif/2/cb%2F37%2F05%2Fcb37051164324250bfe6139c550da5b6%2Fintermediate_file/full/300,/0/default.jpg);background-position: center;background-size: cover;"></div>
				  <div class="gallery-item-content">
					  <h3>Codex Aubin : manuscript, [between 1775 and 1825]</h3>
					  <p style="text-decoration:none;color:black;border-bottom:none;">Manuscript copy of the drawings and the Nahuatl text of the "Codex Aubin," a Mexican Indian pictorial chronicle of Aztec history from the Valley of Mexico, composed at different dates and by different authors, with drawings and Nahuatl text.</p>

				  </div>
				</a>
			    
			
			
			   
				<a href="aztec.html" class="gallery-item">
				  <div class="gallery-item-img" style="background-image:url(https://iiif-cloud.princeton.edu/iiif/2/9a%2F90%2F2f%2F9a902f344e58448198469f8824964b4f%2Fintermediate_file/full/300,/0/default.jpg);background-position: center;background-size: cover;"></div>
				  <div class="gallery-item-content">
					  <h3>Aztec map with glyphs.</h3>
					  <p style="text-decoration:none;color:black;border-bottom:none;">A later copy (18th or 19th century) of a historical map dealing with a migration of the Mexica, or Aztec, from Tollan to Tenochtitlan. </p>

				  </div>
				</a>
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
			
			    
			
 
